text.tspan: Various Short term vocational training courses have been conducted for technical personnel from industry to
upgrade their skill in the specialized field of interest such as veneer peeling, resin manufacture, panel/sheet
manufacture, testing and standardization as well as specific training in the mode of transfer of technologies.
A few courses have also been conducted to train artisans/rural people engaged in bamboo related activities
for mechanized slivering of bamboo required for mat making, NGOs, engineers and architects in bamboo
based housing and entrepreneurs for different bamboo based technologies.
